.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_colour_details -  Returns the array of information stored about a particular colour.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int * query_colour_details(string word)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^word%^RESET%^ - The colour in question
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/cmr_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Returns the array of information stored about a particular colour. The
array is setup using add_colour.

.EP

